  "title": "Every widget implementation should have his own page",
  "body": "- HitsPerPage\n- HitsPerPageSelect\n- Range\n- Range.Ratings\n\nAnd possibly others, all have different props API even if some props are similar. We should provide them individual pages instead of trying to have them in the same documentation page.\n\nThis issues is linked to the default export strategy #1303, since the later will require creating new directories, new READMEs. That will help this issue.\n",
